des:
Create simple Spread Sheet using your voice.
Export it as CSV document and receive via email.
Update the document with new lines and re-export.
Clone (copy) document structure from existing documents.
Change document name.
Delete document.
Compatible with Microsoft Excel and Google Sheets.

** List of commands **
'Alexa, open Work Books'

'Alexa, open Work Books and create new'
'Alexa, open Work Books and create new document'

'Alexa, open Work Books and edit document'
'Alexa, open Work Books and add to document'

'Alexa, open Work Books and rename document'

'Alexa, open Work Books and delete document'

'Alexa, open Work Books and export document'
'Alexa, open Work Books and post'
'Alexa, open Work Books and send'
'Alexa, open Work Books and email'

'Alexa, open Work Books and copy document'
